author: Paul Blest, VICE News
title: Prince Charles Has Coronavirus
description: The 71-year-old heir to the British throne says he has mild symptoms.
content:
Prince Charles, the 71-year old heir to the British throne, has tested positive for coronavirus, according to a statement from Clarence House.
